---

<section class="section tw-section">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="eyebrow">CHAT INTERFACE //</div>
		<h2 class="section-title">ThreadWeaver — multi-provider chat, built for local AI.</h2>
		<p class="section-lede">
			ThreadWeaver is the chat interface that ships with PicoCluster Claw.
			It runs on top of the AgentStateGraph (ASG) substrate and connects
			to local models on Crush, cloud APIs, or both — your choice every session.
		</p>

		<div class="features-row">
			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon icon-blue">⚡</div>
				<div class="feature-body">
					<h3>5+ model providers</h3>
					<p>
						Switch between Ollama (local), OpenAI, Anthropic, Mistral,
						and Groq from the same interface. No separate installs —
						credentials live in one config, models are one click away.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon icon-blue">🧠</div>
				<div class="feature-body">
					<h3>ASG substrate</h3>
					<p>
						Threads are backed by the
						<a href="https://github.com/picocluster/asg" rel="noopener">AgentStateGraph</a>
						— not a flat JSON log. Conversations are stateful, resumable,
						and searchable without any extra setup.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon icon-blue">🔧</div>
				<div class="feature-body">
					<h3>Native Python hooks + filter</h3>
					<p>
						Drop a Python function into the hook directory and it runs
						on every message — pre-send, post-receive, or both.
						ThreadWeaver's MCP + ASG + filter pipeline means you
						control what the model sees.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon icon-red">🔒</div>
				<div class="feature-body">
					<h3>Encryption at rest</h3>
					<p>
						All conversation history is encrypted on disk.
						Local models never leave the cluster. Cloud calls
						are opt-in — you decide per-thread, not system-wide.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="pipeline-box">
			<div class="pipeline-label">ThreadWeaver pipeline</div>
			<div class="pipeline">
				<div class="stage">MCP tools</div>
				<div class="arrow">→</div>
				<div class="stage stage-blue">ASG state</div>
				<div class="arrow">→</div>
				<div class="stage">filter hooks</div>
				<div class="arrow">→</div>
				<div class="stage stage-model">model</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.tw-section {
		background:
			radial-gradient(
				ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 50%,
				rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.05),
				transparent 60%
			),
			var(--ctx-bg);
	}

	.eyebrow {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
		background: rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.08);
		border: 1px solid rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.28);
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.features-row {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1.25rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.feature {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		background: var(--ctx-panel);
		border: 1px solid var(--ctx-border);
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-lg);
		padding: 1.25rem;
	}

	.feature-icon {
		width: 2.25rem;
		height: 2.25rem;
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-md);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-size: 1rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.icon-blue {
		background: var(--claw-blue-dim);
		border: 1px solid rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.3);
	}

	.icon-red {
		background: var(--claw-red-dim);
		border: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.25);
	}

	.feature-body h3 {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin: 0 0 0.4rem 0;
	}

	.feature-body p {
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.pipeline-box {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		background: var(--ctx-panel);
		border: 1px solid var(--ctx-border-hi);
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-lg);
		padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
	}

	.pipeline-label {
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--ctx-text-faint);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
	}

	.pipeline {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.stage {
		padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
		background: var(--ctx-panel-hi);
		border: 1px solid var(--ctx-border-hi);
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-md);
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
	}

	.stage-blue {
		border-color: rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.4);
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
	}

	.stage-model {
		border-color: var(--ctx-border-hi);
		color: #ffffff;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.arrow {
		color: var(--ctx-text-faint);
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.features-row {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		.feature {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
